 needs to transform itself

931
00:39:45,480 --> 00:39:47,610
into a DNA copy

932
00:39:47,650 --> 00:39:49,110
in order to knit itself

933
00:39:49,150 --> 00:39:52,610
into the nuclear DNA 
 of the newly infected cell.

934
00:39:52,650 --> 00:39:56,280
