 has the ability

953
00:40:42,540 --> 00:40:45,330
to make those component pieces 
 that it needs to make

954
00:40:45,370 --> 00:40:46,670
in order to self-assemble

955
00:40:46,710 --> 00:40:49,040
and make 
 an infectious viral particle.

